Former Public Protector, Thuli Madonsela has voiced her opinion on the deployment of former eThekwini mayor as a member of the KwaZulu-Natal legislature. Courtesy #DStv403 DURBAN - Former Public Protector, Thuli Madonsela said she’s disappointed that the former eThekwini mayor is now a member of the KwaZulu-Natal legislature. ANC KZN: Gumede innocent until proven guilty Zandile Gumede was sworn in on Wednesday, replacing the late Ricardo Mthembu. Madonsela said the ANC must get its house in order if it wants to regain public trust. Gumede is being investigated for corruption and fraud relating to a R208-million tender scandal.